wiki.text:
'AOB' is a three-letter abbreviation with multiple meanings, as described below:
* "Any Other Business" - an agenda item for free miscellaneous points
* Accessory olfactory bulb, the dorsal-posterior region of the main
  olfactory bulb.
* Ace of Base
* Alcohol On Breath, a medical sign of alcohol consumption
* Angle On the Bow, a variable in nautical rangekeeping
* Antioxidant of bamboo leaves
* Antyfaszystowska Organizacja Bojowa
* Anterior Open Bite, a term used in dentistry
* Austin O'Brien Catholic High School, a Catholic Senior High School in
  Edmonton, Alberta, Canada
* Array of Bytes (AoB)

'aob' may refer to :
* Abom language ISO 639-3 code
